    "If the pretrained model does not have a strong grasp of semantic knowledge or lacks certain linguistic skills, the effectiveness of SK-Tuning could be reduced.",
    "It needs significant training to accurately understand the semantic meaning of the prompt or prefix text.",
    "The effectiveness of SK-Tuning depends on using prompts or prefixes that are meaningful.",
    "The more relevant the prompt is to the task, the better the performance, described in section \"Effect of prompt and prefix text\".",
    "However, creating or finding these meaningful prompts can be difficult and might require specific knowledge about the domain."
